00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:06,780
 as believers of Jesus, we know the truth.

520
00:23:06,780 --> 00:23:09,180
 Now the enemy, his schemes, right?

521
00:23:09,180 --> 00:23:10,540
 He hates the truth.

522
00:23:10,540 --> 00:23:13,860
 John 8, 44 tells us that the enemy

523
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:18,220
 is a liar and the father of lies.

524
00:23:18,220 --> 00:23:20,300
 The enemy hates the truth.

525
00:23:20,300 --> 00:23:23,580
 But this is why we have to say it even more clearly.

526
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:26,100
 So let me remind us, church, of the truth.

527
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:28,420
 The truth is that Jesus loves you

528
00:23:28,420 --> 00:23:30,740
 and he died for your sins.

529
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:34,580
 The truth is he is alive and resurrected.

530
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:36,580
 The truth that he has called you to live a life

531
00:23:36,580 --> 00:23:41,300
 that reflects and shows his love to those around us.

532
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:43,500
 The truth is even though there are these other

533
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:46,620
 spiritual beings, there is only one true,

534
00:23:46,620 --> 00:23:49,580
 all-powerful, almighty God.

535
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:54,500
 And the truth is the war has already been won.

536
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:57,940
 Jesus, over on this earth, is progressing

537
00:23:57,940 --> 00:24:00,860
 and advancing against these unseen powers of darkness

538
00:24:00,860 --> 00:24:03,700
 and the kingdom of God has a very clear goal

539
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:05,460
 and it will reach this goal.

540
00:24:05,460 --> 00:24:08,180
 The reclamation of all peoples and all nations,

541
00:24:08,180 --> 00:24:10,260
 the full restoration of God's creation

542
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:13,260
 to how he originally created it to be.

543
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:15,620
 This day is coming.

544
00:24:15,620 --> 00:24:18,940
 That is the truth, church, and the truth doesn't change.

545
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:22,420
 So church, do you have this belt of truth

546
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:24,340
 buckled around you?

547
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:27,180
 Does the truth of who Jesus is and what he has done

548
00:24:27,180 --> 00:24:31,660
 for you and all humanity hold your life together?

549
00:24:31,660 --> 00:24:35,060
 Wrap this truth around yourself tightly.

550
00:24:35,060 --> 00:24:39,580
 Buckle up because without it, everything will fall apart.

551
00:24:39,580 --> 00:24:45,540
 Then it talks about the breastplate of righteousness.

552
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:47,940
 Now the breastplate is the largest piece

553
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:52,820
 of the Roman soldier's armor, protects the vital organs,

554
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:55,100
 the heart, the lungs, all that kind of stuff.

555
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:57,020
 But because the breastplate is the biggest,

556
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:59,140
 it's the most obvious part.

557
00:24:59,140 --> 00:25:01,140
 It's the part that everyone can see.

558
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:03,020
 It's the most prominent thing.

559
00:25:03,020 --> 00:25:06,940
 And so in our context, in what we're talking about here,

560
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:11,660
 for us, this means God has called us to proudly display

561
00:25:11,660 --> 00:25:15,700
 the fact that we are followers of Jesus,

562
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:19,020
 that we are children of the light,

563
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:22,420
 that we walk in righteousness.

564
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:25,460
 Now the opposite of righteousness is wickedness.

565
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:30,380
 And the enemy, that's what he delights in, in wickedness.

566
00:25:30,380 --> 00:25:34,020
 Scripture tells us that the enemy is an oppressor.

567
00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:37,700
 The enemy is the orchestrator of injustice.

568
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:41,340
 The enemy would like to see us do unrighteous things,

569
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:43,620
 unholy things to each other.

570
00:25:43,620 --> 00:25:45,540
 Then the enemy wants us to abuse

571
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:47,820
 and to take advantage of each other.

572
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:49,780
 That's wickedness.

573
00:25:49,780 --> 00:25:52,380
 That's how the enemy's schemes work.

574
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:55,660
 But when we put on the breastplate of righteousness,

575
00:25:55,660 --> 00:25:59,180
 it means that we are in right standing with God,

576
00:25:59,180 --> 00:26:02,820
 which also means we are living out God's justice

577
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,700
 in his battle against evil.

578
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:09,780
 So church, put on this breastplate of righteousness.

579
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:13,700
 We are called to live a life that reflects God's heart

580
00:26:13,700 --> 00:26:16,540
 for the weak and the oppressed.

581
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:19,060
 We are called to speak out and do something

582
00:26:19,060 --> 00:26:23,380
 when a situation doesn't fit in to what God's heart is.

583
00:26:23,380 --> 00:26:25,340
 We are called to act justly,

584
00:26:25,340 --> 00:26:29,620
 just as God is just and righteous.

585
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:34,860
 So we put on this breastplate so we can be the people of God

586
00:26:34,860 --> 00:26:36,380
 that he has called us to be.

587
00:26:36,380 --> 00:26:40,500
 People who walk alongside the weak and the oppressed,

588
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:43,260
 who look after the widows and the orphans,

589
00:26:43,260 --> 00:26:46,460
 a voice of justice in a world that's unjust,

590
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:50,820
 a people who are unashamedly living for the gospel,

591
00:26:50,820 --> 00:26:53,740
 proudly declaring who they are.

592
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:55,820
 Put on this breastplate of righteousness

593
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:57,940
 and wear it proudly, church.

594
00:26:57,940 --> 00:27:03,300
 Then it tells us, the feet fitted with the readiness

595
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:05,700
 that comes from the gospel of peace.

596
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:08,660
 So much of a soldier's life, right,

597
00:27:08,660 --> 00:27:11,900
 you can imagine is either spent standing firm,

598
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:13,740
 standing in one place, keeping guard,

599
00:27:13,740 --> 00:27:16,780
 or requiring them to march forward

600
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:18,300
 and move to a different place.

601
00:27:18,300 --> 00:27:21,940
 Both require strong, steady shoes.

602
00:27:21,940 --> 00:27:24,260
 And time and time again, you have heard it repeated,

603
00:27:24,260 --> 00:27:26,460
 the call has been to stand firm,

604
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:29,340
 stand firm, to be unmoved.

605
00:27:29,340 --> 00:27:33,700
 You see, the enemy doesn't want us to stand firm.

606
00:27:33,700 --> 00:27:37,740
 The enemy wants to make us change our minds.

607
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:38,820
 That's another one of his schemes,

608
00:27:38,820 --> 00:27:41,660
 especially in our relationship with Jesus.

609
00:27:41,660 --> 00:27:45,340
 The enemy knows that a double-minded person

610
00:27:45,340 --> 00:27:48,300
 is unstable in all that they do.

611
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,660
 James 1:8 tells us that.

612
00:27:49,660 --> 00:27:52,700
 And so what he wants to do,

613
00:27:52,700 --> 00:27:56,060
 he likes nothing more than to make us second guess

614
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:59,260
 Jesus' love for us, his plans for us,

615
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:03,380
 to get us to doubt what God has already told us.

616
00:28:03,380 --> 00:28:07,260
 In other words, to disrupt the peace that you feel

617
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:09,300
 when you have the word of God,

618
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:12,300
 when you have Jesus living with you and in you

619
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:14,380
 that comes from following the Lord.

620
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:19,220
 Do you feel like you can relate to this?

621
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:23,220
 Have you ever felt yourself doubting the goodness of God?

622
00:28:23,220 --> 00:28:24,780
 Right at the beginning, that was his scheme, right?

623
00:28:24,780 --> 00:28:27,220
 He said to Eve, did God really say this?

624
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:30,020
 Trying to get her to change her mind?

