00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:44,060
 I felt like with my school friends,

631
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:46,300
 and in one context I was this person,

632
00:28:46,300 --> 00:28:48,620
 but in another context I was the good church boy

633
00:28:48,620 --> 00:28:51,500
 and it was so hard trying to navigate my life

634
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:53,180
 between the two identities

635
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,980
 that I seemed to carry at that time.

636
00:28:54,980 --> 00:29:00,340
 Do you ever hear the enemy make you doubt

637
00:29:00,340 --> 00:29:03,860
 if God really has given you the peace he has promised you?

638
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:10,020
 We need to fit our feet in the gospel

639
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:12,100
 because the gospel is the only thing

640
00:29:12,100 --> 00:29:15,420
 that gives us a firm foundation to stand on,

641
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:16,920
 to build our lives upon.

642
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:19,420
 Jesus said this before he left earth,

643
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:22,900
 peace I leave with you, my peace I give to you,

644
00:29:22,900 --> 00:29:25,780
 not as the world gives do I give to you.

645
00:29:25,780 --> 00:29:28,020
 Let not your hearts be troubled,

646
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:30,260
 neither let them be afraid.

647
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:33,740
 So we fit our feet with the gospel

648
00:29:33,740 --> 00:29:35,900
 so that we can have a firm place to stand

649
00:29:35,900 --> 00:29:37,180
 and to build our life.

650
00:29:37,180 --> 00:29:39,060
 But here's the other thing,

651
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:41,900
 at the same time, knowing the gospel

652
00:29:41,900 --> 00:29:44,260
 also allows us to bring this peace

653
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:48,380
 to areas of conflict, to areas that need it.

654
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:50,620
 We have been called to stand firm, yes,

655
00:29:50,620 --> 00:29:55,420
 but sometimes offense is the best version of defense.

656
00:29:55,420 --> 00:29:58,140
 And when we see there's a place that needs the gospel,

657
00:29:58,140 --> 00:29:59,820
 when we see our family and our friends,

658
00:29:59,820 --> 00:30:04,260
 when we see areas of this society that needs peace,

