00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:06,220
 then we are called to carry it there.

660
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:09,900
 And when that moment comes for you to carry the gospel,

661
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:12,580
 to live out the gospel, to speak the gospel,

662
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:15,060
 we also need to be ready for those moments

663
00:30:15,060 --> 00:30:17,700
 whenever opportunity presents itself.

664
00:30:17,700 --> 00:30:20,820
 Whenever God calls you,

665
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:23,660
 will you be able to respond like Isaiah and say,

666
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:27,020
 Lord, here I am, send me.

667
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:29,940
 So we put on the gospel,

668
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:32,660
 we fit our feet with the gospel of peace

669
00:30:32,660 --> 00:30:35,060
 so that we cannot just stand firm,

670
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:38,780
 but also bring the gospel to those places that need it.

671
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:43,740
 Then it says we need to take up the shield of faith

672
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,700
 with which you can extinguish

673
00:30:45,700 --> 00:30:49,100
 all the flaming arrows of the evil one.

674
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:50,420
 So the shields for Roman soldier

675
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:52,460
 were probably about like four feet high,

676
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:53,980
 about as wide as a body,

677
00:30:53,980 --> 00:30:55,380
 a cover up most of the upper body.

678
00:30:55,380 --> 00:30:57,180
 They were important because

679
00:30:57,180 --> 00:30:59,380
 one of the most common methods of attack back then

680
00:30:59,380 --> 00:31:02,460
 was to dip arrows in tar and light it.

681
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:03,780
 You've probably seen it in the movies, right?

682
00:31:03,780 --> 00:31:06,780
 These flaming arrows, literally flaming arrows that come

683
00:31:06,780 --> 00:31:08,980
 and so like with the sword, you can,

684
00:31:08,980 --> 00:31:12,660
 with a shield, you can block the enemy's attacks.

685
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:16,780
 The shields will have a special covering on the top,

686
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:18,540
 like a leather, so the shield itself

687
00:31:18,540 --> 00:31:21,260
 wouldn't sort of burn up as well.

688
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:22,460
 Google it, I don't know.

689
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:25,300
 For us, this is what's important, okay?

690
00:31:26,460 --> 00:31:30,340
 The shield of faith talks about our faith

691
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:34,060
 and our loyalty to Jesus, no matter what.

692
00:31:34,060 --> 00:31:38,020
 The enemy is a master archer,

693
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:41,860
 and like we said, he fires, all things kind of schemes.

694
00:31:41,860 --> 00:31:45,540
 His arrows he fires at us are things like doubt,

695
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:50,540
 things like fear, selfishness, impurity, lust, greed,

696
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:54,340
 adverse circumstances, pride, self-confidence,

697
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:57,140
 persecution, false teaching, all these things,

698
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:58,300
 the list could go on.

699
00:31:58,300 --> 00:32:02,220
 These arrows are there to make us doubt what we believe in.

700
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:07,140
 His arrows are designed to try and burn down our faith.

701
00:32:07,140 --> 00:32:13,940
 But the shield reminds us that we walk by faith

702
00:32:13,940 --> 00:32:16,220
 and not by sight.

703
00:32:16,220 --> 00:32:18,660
 So even as the enemy fires these arrows,

704
00:32:18,660 --> 00:32:21,980
 we put up our faith, we put up our loyalty to Jesus,

705
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:24,260
 and they will be extinguished.

706
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:27,260
 Even when we do not fully see or understand

707
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:29,940
 what is happening, faith is acknowledging

708
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:33,060
 that God's ways are higher than our ways.

709
00:32:33,060 --> 00:32:37,180
 And in this battle, we cannot defer, we cannot jump ship.

710
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:39,980
 We have to stay loyal to Jesus.

711
00:32:39,980 --> 00:32:43,700
 One of the most amazing displays of faith and loyalty,

712
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:45,940
 I think, in scripture is through the story

713
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:49,260
 of Daniel's friends, Shadrach, Meshach, and Abednego

714
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:51,660
 in the book of Daniel.

715
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:54,700
 Here they are facing the fiery furnace,

716
00:32:54,700 --> 00:32:56,460
 and these are their words.

717
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:59,660
 "If we are thrown into the blazing furnace,

718
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:02,300
 "the God we serve is able to deliver us from it,

719
00:33:02,300 --> 00:33:04,180
 "and he will deliver us."

720
00:33:04,180 --> 00:33:05,140
 That's the faith.

721
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:10,060
 "But even if he does not, we want you to know,

722
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:12,500
 "your majesty, that we will not serve your gods

723
00:33:12,500 --> 00:33:15,060
 "or worship the image of gold you have set up."

724
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:17,060
 That's the loyalty.

725
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:21,900
 So church, we have been called to hold on tight

726
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:26,620
 to the shield of faith, and to loyally follow Jesus

727
00:33:26,620 --> 00:33:31,220
 into battle, extinguishing all the flaming arrows

728
00:33:31,220 --> 00:33:32,060
 of the enemy.

729
00:33:32,060 --> 00:33:38,820
 Then it tells us about the helmet of salvation.

730
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:40,380
 Right, for the soldier, the helmet covers

731
00:33:40,380 --> 00:33:42,860
 another important part of the body, the head.

732
00:33:42,860 --> 00:33:45,460
 And the helmet was also sometimes a way of determining

733
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:47,300
 the position and the rank of the soldier,

734
00:33:47,300 --> 00:33:50,100
 these plumes on the top of the helmet.

735
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:56,220
 And so for us, this helmet speaks to our identity.

736
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:59,460
 It's knowing who you belong to.

737
00:33:59,460 --> 00:34:03,580
 As you battle, as you take your stand,

738
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:06,900
 know that you are fighting for King Jesus.

739
00:34:06,900 --> 00:34:10,500
 That as brothers and sisters, as people of Christ,

740
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:13,780
 we are part of the Lord's army.

741
00:34:13,780 --> 00:34:15,300
 And with the helmet of salvation,

742
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:17,220
 and what that does, it's that reminds us

743
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:20,460
 that we have already been saved.

744
00:34:20,460 --> 00:34:23,860
 This is one of the most important things to hold on to.

745
00:34:23,860 --> 00:34:26,380
 All these things that the enemy's trying to do,

746
00:34:26,380 --> 00:34:29,220
 ultimately, they're not gonna change the outcome.

747
00:34:29,220 --> 00:34:32,700
 Right, we said this just now, Jesus is already victorious.

748
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:37,580
 He's doing everything he can to try and distract us

749
00:34:37,580 --> 00:34:38,420
 from this fact.

750
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:40,940
 But through his death and resurrection,

751
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:42,940
 Jesus has already won.

752
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:46,060
 He has already overcome sin and death.

753
00:34:46,060 --> 00:34:50,260
 And the enemy's not attacking from a place of strength,

754
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:53,980
 but from a place of already having been defeated.

755
00:34:53,980 --> 00:34:56,660
 Well, we have to realize this,

756
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:59,220
 the enemy is a desperate loser.

757
00:34:59,220 --> 00:35:03,580
 In this time, he might have some influence on earth,

758
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:06,820
 but his fate has already been sealed.

759
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:08,900
 And when Jesus returns, when the new heaven

760
00:35:08,900 --> 00:35:10,460
 and the new earth comes,

761
00:35:10,740 --> 00:35:12,260
 the enemy and all his deeds

762
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:15,420
 and all these other spiritual forces,

763
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,780
 these evil spiritual forces,

764
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:19,540
 will be destroyed once and for all.

765
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:23,580
 And the helmet reminds us that salvation

766
00:35:23,580 --> 00:35:26,660
 and victory belongs to our God.

767
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:28,780
 We are on the winning side.

768
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:31,660
 And so yes, we might get wounded.

769
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:34,700
 We might get hurt.

770
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:36,980
 But following Jesus and doing spiritual battle

771
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:40,260
 against the enemy is not going to be a breeze.

772
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:43,700
 It's not going to be smooth sailing.

773
00:35:43,700 --> 00:35:45,580
 Let's not forget there are people out there,

774
00:35:45,580 --> 00:35:47,660
 other Christians in parts of the world

775
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:49,740
 who are literally being persecuted,

776
00:35:49,740 --> 00:35:53,820
 literally risking their lives for the sake of the gospel.

777
00:35:53,820 --> 00:35:57,300
 But even in that situation,

778
00:35:57,300 --> 00:36:00,140
 the helmet of salvation reminds us,

779
00:36:00,140 --> 00:36:03,180
